2018.03 Deprecated Packages

  • Start Date: 2018-03-31
  • End Date:
  • Full list of packages

https://aws.amazon.com/amazon-linux-ami/2018.03-release-notes/

These packages were deprecated with the initial Amazon Linux 2018.03 release announcement and will not receive any further updates. Most were announced nearing EoL in the 2016.09 release notes.

  • Start Date: 2020-01-20
  • End Date:
  • Full list of packages

https://aws.amazon.com/amazon-linux-ami/faqs/

As announced with Maintenance Support, these packages will no longer receive updates. This matches their upstream End of Life.

Amazon Linux 1 End Of Life

  • Start Date: 2023-06-30
  • End Date:
  • Full list of packages

https://aws.amazon.com/amazon-linux-ami/faqs/

The Maintenance Support period of Amazon Linux 1 ends on June 30, 2023. From this point, the remaining Amazon Linux 1 packages (listed below) will no longer receive any updates from AWS.
